description: No sticker machine required! As a stand-alone product, Adhesive Sheets offer crafters the convenience of pre-made adhesive sheets. When used with a Sizzix® roller machine, Adhesive Sheets easily transform crafters' favorite die-cuts into ready-made stickers.

name: Sizzix Big Shot Express Machine
description:
With just the push of a button, the Big Shot™ Express leaves the crank behind. Instead, the motorized Big Shot Express works with the entire Sizzix® product library (with the exception of Bigz™ Plus and Bigz Pro dies) - and that includes our smallest dies to our big 6" wide plastic-backed treasures and embossing tools.

If that wasn't big enough, this portable roller machine cuts and embosses many different materials. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards, invitations, scrapbook pages, home décor, fashion, altered art, quilting and much more! (To ensure compatibility, always check machine and accessory requirements. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Sizzix Big Shot Machine
description:
There's a reason why we call our shape-cutting and embossing machine a Big Shot™. It's because the ever-versatile Big Shot works with the entire Sizzix® product library (with the exception of Bigz™ Plus and Bigz Pro dies) - and that includes our smallest dies to our big 6" wide plastic-backed treasures and embossing tools.

If that wasn't big enough, this portable roller machine cuts and embosses many different materials. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards, invitations, scrapbook pages, home décor, fashion, altered art, quilting and much more! (To ensure compatibility, always check accessory requirements. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Sizzix Big Shot Plus Machine
description:
One shape-cutting machine does it all! The Sizzix® Big Shot™ Plus Machine works with any Sizzix die or embossing folder up to 9" wide to create an amazing assortment of craft shapes.

If that wasn't enough, this powerful roller machine cuts and embosses many different materials. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards, invitations, scrapbook pages, home décor, fashion, altered art, quilting and much more using your favorite 8 1/2" x 11" materials! (To ensure compatibility, always check machine and accessory requirements. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Sizzix Big Shot Pro Machine
description:
One shape-cutting machine does it all! The Sizzix® Big Shot™ Pro Machine works with any Sizzix die or embossing folder to create an amazing assortment of craft shapes. For added versatility, these machines are compatible with SureCut™ dies from our Ellison® education brand, plus most other brands of steel-rule dies.

If that wasn't enough, this industrial strength roller machine cuts and embosses many different materials. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards, invitations, scrapbook pages, home décor, fashion, altered art, quilting and much more! (To ensure compatibility, always check machine and accessory requirements. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Sizzix BIGkick Machine
description:
Give a great BIGkick™ to your creativity! The BIGkick works with the entire Sizzix® product library (with the exception of Bigz™ Plus and Bigz Pro dies) - and that includes our smallest dies to our big 6" wide plastic-backed treasures and embossing tools.

If that wasn't big enough, this portable roller machine cuts and embosses many different materials. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Sizzix Bigz Clear Dies
description:
Our big see-through plastic dies reveal exactly what's being cut. How's that for precision? Bigz™ Clear Dies transform treasured photographs and computer printouts into exciting decorative accents, frames, tags and other spectacular shapes that clearly capture any style.

These oversized dies cut almost anything including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, craft aluminum, and many other materials. Imagine the giant-sized possibilities!

name: Sizzix Bigz Dies
description:
Some of our biggest dies create some of our boldest designs! That's why Bigz™ are so beautiful.

These big dies cut almost anything including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, craft aluminum, and many other materials. Imagine the giant-sized possibilities of our large and lovely decorative shapes, bags, cards, envelopes and lettering!

name: Sizzix Bigz Dies w/Crease
description:
Some of our biggest dies with crease create some of our boldest designs! That's why Bigz™ are so beautiful.

These big dies with crease cut almost anything including cardstock and vellum. Imagine the giant-sized possibilities of our large and lovely bags, boxes, cards and envelopes!

name: Sizzix Bigz L Dies
description: Just a bit bigger than our standard Bigz™ dies, these great big dies cut almost anything, including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, craft aluminum and many other materials. Imagine the giant-sized possibilities of our large and lovely decorative shapes!

name: Sizzix Bigz L Dies w/Crease
description: Just a bit bigger than our standard Bigz™ dies, these great big dies cut almost anything, including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, craft aluminum and many other materials. Imagine the giant-sized possibilities of our large and lovely decorative shapes!

name: Sizzix Bigz Plus Dies
description: They don't get much bigger than this. Bigz™ Plus dies, cut hundreds of materials - including cardstock, chipboard, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, metallic foil, paper and sandpaper (in limited use) - and our biggest shapes, including full-size bags, boxes, cards, envelopes and album covers made exclusively for the Big Shot™ Plus Machine. These dies are also compatible with the Big Shot Pro Machine.

name: Sizzix Bigz Plus Dies w/Crease
description:
They don't get much bigger than this. Bigz™ Plus dies, cut hundreds of materials - including cardstock, chipboard, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, metallic foil, paper and sandpaper (in limited use) - and our biggest shapes, including full-size bags, boxes, cards, envelopes and album covers made exclusively for the Big Shot™ Plus Machine. These dies are also compatible with the Big Shot Pro Machine.

Actual die design may be angled. In order to produce the best results when cutting on patterned paper containing stripes, orient the paper so it lines up with the cut blades and not the edge of the die.

name: Sizzix Bigz Pro 25" Dies
description: They don't get any bigger than this. Bigz™ Pro 25" dies, our largest dies ever, cut hundreds of materials - including cardstock, chipboard, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, metallic foil, paper and sandpaper (in limited use) - and our biggest shapes. Designed exclusively for the Big Shot™ Pro Machine, these dies are great for cutting fast quilting designs.

name: Sizzix Bigz Pro Dies
description:
They don't get any bigger than this. Bigz™ Pro dies, our largest dies ever, cut hundreds of materials - including cardstock, chipboard, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, metallic foil, paper and sandpaper (in limited use) - and our biggest shapes, including full-size bags, boxes, cards, envelopes and album covers made exclusively for the Big Shot™ Pro Machine.

Actual die design may be angled. In order to produce the best results when cutting on patterned paper containing stripes, orient the paper so it lines up with the cut blades and not the edge of the die.

name: Sizzix Bigz XL 25" Dies
description: They don't get much bigger than this. Bigz™ XL 25" dies, our longest dies ever, cut hundreds of materials - including cardstock, chipboard, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, metallic foil, paper and sandpaper (in limited use) - and our biggest shapes. These dies are great for cutting fast quilting designs.

name: Sizzix Bigz XL Dies
description:
It's big news! Our bigger dies create easy-to-assemble projects, while featuring simple crease-rule marks for fast folding.'

These great big dies cut almost anything including cardstock, felt, 'fabric, foam, magnet, leather, craft aluminum, and many other materials.' Imagine the giant-sized possibilities of our large and lovely 'decorative shapes, bags, cards, envelopes and lettering!

name: Sizzix Bigz XL Dies w/Crease
description:
It's big news! Our bigger dies create easy-to-assemble projects, while featuring simple crease-rule marks for fast folding.

These great big dies cut almost anything including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather, craft aluminum, and many other materials. Imagine the giant-sized possibilities of our large and lovely decorative shapes, bags, cards, envelopes and lettering!

name: Sizzix Clear Stamps
description: See what you stamp. Stamp what you see. Clear Stamps complement many Sizzix® die designs. Simply stick one of the Clear Stamps onto the Acrylic Stamp Mount for easy, see-through positioning and a handmade stamp that screams style!

name: Sizzix Clearlits Dies
description:
When it comes to cutting and cropping your cherished photos, patterned paper, stamped images and ink-jet printouts of selected words and images, you want precision.

For these reasons, Clearlits™ combine a see-through plastic die back with an essential shape to reveal exactly what's being cut. Now your photos come to life as exciting decorative accents, tags, ornaments, frames and anything else that expresses you! Clearlits Dies are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines. For more information, watch this video: Using Clearlits Dies.

name: Sizzix DecoEmboss Dies
description:
Each DecoEmboss™ Die elegantly embosses beautiful designs onto different shapes of Vintaj® metal blanks. Try one to create or decorate unique metal embellishments for personalized projects such as jewelry, cards, scrapbook pages, boxes, frames and much more. To highlight the raised areas of the blank, use the Vintaj Metal Reliefing block. For different design possibilities with a DecoEmboss Die, place the metal blank onto varying areas of the die with each use. (This gives the added benefit of more even wear.)

DecoEmboss Dies are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines when used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform. For more information, watch this video: Using DecoEmboss Dies.

name: Sizzix DecoEtch Dies
description:
Each DecoEtch die instantly etches (without the use of chemicals) intricate patterns onto different shapes of Vintaj metal blanks. Try one to create or decorate unique metal embellishments for personalized projects such as jewelry, cards, scrapbook pages, boxes, frames and much more. To highlight the raised areas of the blank, use the Vintaj Metal Reliefing block. For different design possibilities with a DecoEtch Die, place the metal blank onto varying areas of the die with each use. (This gives the added benefit of more even wear.)

DecoEtch Dies are compatible with Big Shot, BIGkick and Vagabond Machines when used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform. For more information, watch this video: Using DecoEtch Dies.

name: Sizzix eclips Cartridges
description: Getting new Sizzix® artwork for your eclips® machine is as easy as inserting a new cartridge! Preloaded with excellent features specially adapted for electronic shape-cutting - including cutting solids, shadows, borders, outlines, pieces and embellishments - the eclips Cartridge easily allows you to change your theme and your possibilities.

name: Sizzix eclips Machine
description:
Take a look at a total eclips®! The eclips is the first electronic shape-cutting machine to combine the creativity of Sizzix® artwork with amazing cutting, scoring and drawing precision and remote-controlled intelligence. This machine creates completely customizable shapes and letters to make cards, envelopes, scrapbook pages, bags, boxes, home décor projects, fashion accessories, altered art and much more!

With the Stamp2Cut™ cartridges, you can cut around Tim Holtz® Stampers Anonymous stamps. Another creative option is eCAL software which works with your computer to create and modify your own designs and then works with the eclips to cut, score or draw the shapes.

name: Sizzix eclips Stamp2Cut Cartridges
description: Combining the creativity of Tim Holtz® and the Sizzix® eclips® Electronic Shape-Cutting Machine, eclips Stamp2Cut™ cartridges create the quickest and easiest cuts around Tim's Stampers Anonymous stamped images. Forget complicated cutting with a pair of scissors, this time-saving innovation makes it a breeze to cut multiples of a shape with electronic precision, while adding a whole new dimension to your stamping. For the most accurate registration, each design includes a cutting template with original, solid, shadow and pieces (on selected designs).

name: Sizzix eclips2 Machine
description:
With no cartridges required, the newly redesigned eclips®2 DIY Electronic Cutter contains an enhanced motor with industrial-strength gears for speed, reduced noise, efficiency, precision cutting and more. In addition, the eclips2 is accompanied by free eCAL lite software to create your own designs, plus cut, score and draw/edit unique shapes for beautiful customized projects from the start.

With the eclips2 and eCAL lite, you can weld multiple shapes and letters into one cut. Use Appearance Styles, like Shadow and Blackout, to quickly change the look of letters and shapes. You can also access TrueType, OpenType and fonts currently installed on your computer, including Dingbat/Wingding fonts.

name: Sizzix Embosslits Dies
description:
Cut. Emboss. Create. It takes just one magical step to make perfectly cut shapes with an elegant embossed flair.

Embosslits™ combine cutting and embossing into one easy step and make papercrafting embellishments a snap. For a dash of sass, add them to your next thank you cards and envelopes, shower place cards, gift bags, journal covers and anything else that needs a little hocus pocus.

Most Embosslits work in the entire family of Sizzix® machines, but some are compatible with roller machines only (where noted).

name: Sizzix Embosslits XL Dies
description:
Cut. Emboss. Create. It takes just one magical step to make perfectly cut shapes with an elegant embossed flair.

Embosslits™ combine cutting and embossing into one easy step and make papercrafting embellishments a snap. For a dash of sass, add them to your next thank you cards and envelopes, shower place cards, gift bags, journal covers and anything else that needs a little hocus pocus.

Most Embosslits work in the entire family of Sizzix® machines, but some are compatible with roller machines only (where noted).

name: Sizzix Framelits Die Sets
description: What you see is what you get with Framelits™: easy cropping of photos, precise cutting of windows in a card and even 3-D layering. In addition, the design of a Framelits Die allows for perfect registration (with no ridges to obscure), which is useful for stamped images or sentiments. For use in the larger Sizzix® roller machines with the machine's included platform; when using the Essentials Platform or Solo Platform & Shim, the Extended Adapter or Solo Adapter is required. All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Framelits Die Sets w/Stamps
description:
What you see is what you get with Framelits™: easy cropping of photos, precise cutting of windows in a card and even 3-D layering. In addition, the design of a Framelits Die allows for perfect registration (with no ridges to obscure), which is useful for stamped images or sentiments. For use in the larger Sizzix® roller machines with the machine's included platform; when using the Essentials Platform or Solo Platform & Shim, the Extended Adapter or Solo Adapter is required. All items sold separately.

Looking for perfect registration with stamps? These Framelits Die Sets come with a matching stamp set to complement your next project.

name: Sizzix Framelits Die Sets w/Textured Impressions
description: The combination of a Framelits™ Die Set and Textured Impressions™ Embossing Folder Set allows you to create the most exact cuts around your embossed images. It's that easy and efficient with Framelits. These wafer-thin, chemical-etched die sets feature the perfect registration without interference from any ridges at the edge of the die opening. Plus, they're excellent for clearly cropping the images and sentiments created by their coordinating (and included) Textured Impressions Embossing Folders.

name: Sizzix Framelits Plus Die Sets
description: What you see is what you get with Framelits™: easy cropping of photos, precise cutting of windows in a card and even 3-D layering. In addition, the design of a Framelits Die allows for perfect registration (with no ridges to obscure), which is useful for stamped images or sentiments. For use in the Sizzix® Big Shot™ Plus or Big Shot Pro machines. All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Frameworks Dies
description:
Creativity has many facets. With Frameworks™ Dies, you can create distinctive backgrounds with various artistic elements by using the shape as a repeating pattern or smaller die-cuts for accents. Combine both for unlimited mixed-media possibilities! Frameworks cut many materials, including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather and craft aluminum.

Frameworks Dies are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines. For ease of use, we recommend using the specially-sized On the Edge™ or SophistiCut™ Cutting Pads.

name: Sizzix Ink-its Letterpress Plates (A7 Border)
description: Combining style and ease to create artful ink-debossed impressions, Ink-its™ A7 Border Letterpress Plates easily impress paper, cardstock, chipboard, mat board, leather, vinyl, clay and other soft, thick materials. They also provide the perfect accents for elegant cards, invites, scrapbook pages and more. Ink-its Letterpress Plates are compatible with larger Sizzix® roller machines.

name: Sizzix Ink-its Letterpress Plates (A7 Large)
description: Combining style and ease to create artful ink-debossed impressions, Ink-its™ A7 Large Letterpress Plates easily impress paper, cardstock, chipboard, mat board, leather, vinyl, clay and other soft, thick materials. They also provide the perfect accents for elegant cards, invites, scrapbook pages and more. Ink-its Letterpress Plates are compatible with larger Sizzix® roller machines.

name: Sizzix Inksheets Transfer Film
description:
Make a better first impression with Sizzix Inksheets™! Now you can add a whole new dimension to your creativity by creating perfect, smudge-free dry ink impressions. Inksheets can be used with cardstock, craft foil, leather, magnet sheet, plastic, suede, shrink plastic, sponge and wood paper to easily simulate the popular metallic foil and chalkboard looks.

Sizzix Inksheets easily transfer ink onto your projects with three fun ways to create: cut and color at once with wafer-thin, chemical-etched dies, add all over designs embossing folders or personalize with a handwritten message or doodle.

name: Sizzix Little Sizzles
description: For an extraordinary creative system, no ordinary papers will do. Little Sizzles™ Papers are custom made for the unique dimensions of Sizzix® machines and dies. They're available in a variety of color schemes.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers Accessories
description: Extend the use of your Movers & Shapers™ Magnetic Dies with the Movers & Shapers Base Tray, which allows crafters the convenience of a larger cutting area to arrange and move the Magnetic Dies in as many different positions as possible.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers Dies
description: Alter your journey a bit and base your customizable creations with Movers & Shapers Base Dies. For use with Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies (sold separately) or special ejection foam, which is included with all Movers & Shapers Dies. The movable magnetic dies create a window anywhere you want in the base shape for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

description: Alter your journey a bit and base your customizable creations with Movers & Shapers™ Base Dies. The movable magnetic dies create a window anywhere you want in the base shape for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

description: Alter your journey a bit and base your customizable creations with Movers & Shapers™ L Base Dies. The movable magnetic dies create a window anywhere you want in the base shape for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers L Dies w/Crease
description: Alter your journey a bit and base your customizable creations with Movers & Shapers™ L Base Dies. For use with Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies (sold separately) or special ejection foam, which is included with all Movers & Shapers Dies. The movable magnetic dies create a window anywhere you want in the base shape for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies
description:
Sizzix® Movers & Shapers™ are creativity in motion! With these movable magnetic dies, now you can create a window anywhere you want for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

The window die must be used in any one of the Movers & Shapers base dies or base trays, which are compatible with the BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ machines (with a pair of appropriately sized Cutting Pads). All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies w/Crease
description:
Sizzix® Movers & Shapers™ are creativity in motion! With these movable magnetic dies, now you can create a window anywhere you want for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

The window die must be used in any one of the Movers & Shapers base dies or base trays, which are compatible with the BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ machines (with a pair of appropriately sized Cutting Pads). All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers Pro Dies
description:
Creativity is always a moving experience; base your customizable creations on Movers & Shapers™ Pro Die and Die Sets. These dies and die sets offer plenty of dynamic design choices for customizable cards or envelopes.

The movable magnetic dies (included with each die set and also sold separately) create a window anywhere you want in the base shape for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

name: Sizzix Movers & Shapers XL Dies
description:
Creativity is always a moving experience; base your customizable creations on Movers & Shapers™ XL Die Sets. These die sets offer plenty of dynamic design choices for customizable cards.

The movable magnetic dies (included with each die set and also sold separately) create a window anywhere you want in the base shape for a truly customized shape-cutting experience.

name: Sizzix On the Edge Dies
description:
True to their name, these oh-so-edgy dies cut eye-popping edges for cards, mini books, scrapbook pages and more. On each die are one or two unique edges that can be cut on nearly any project up to 5 1/2" wide from nearly any material, including cardstock, felt, fabric, foam, magnet, leather and craft aluminum.

On the Edge Dies™ are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines. For ease of use, we recommend using the specially-sized On the Edge Cutting Pads. For more information, watch this video: Using On the Edge Dies.

name: Sizzix Original Machine
description:
Get ready to be impressed! Our popular press-style machine cuts and embosses with absolute ease.

Along with our Originals™ dies, the original Sizzix® Machine cuts and embosses unforgettable shapes that beautifully embellish cards, scrapbook pages, papercrafts and even clothes!

Add a Sizzix System Converter and elegantly emboss with Simple Impressions® Embossing Folders or cut smaller-sized detailed designs with a mind-boggling selection of Sizzlits® dies that easily cut through cardstock, metallic foil, paper or vellum.

name: Sizzix Originals Dies (Large)
description:
If it's an Originals™ die, then it's like no other. Compatible with our bigger machines, these versatile dies are backed by our thickest blade and most powerful cut. Just one die creates amazing shapes from cardstock, magnet, poly foam, metallic foil, shrink film and even fabric. There's so much to make … including stylish embellishments for scrapbook pages, birthday decorations, holiday cards, invitations, T-shirts, hats and jeans, and the list goes on and on!

Originals dies can be used in the Big Shot™, BIGkick™, Vagabond™ and original Sizzix® machines.

name: Sizzix Originals Dies (Small, Medium & Border)
description:
If it's an Originals™ die, then it's like no other. Compatible with our bigger machines, these versatile dies are backed by our thickest blade and most powerful cut. Just one die creates amazing shapes from cardstock, magnet, poly foam, metallic foil, shrink film and even fabric. There's so much to make … including stylish embellishments for scrapbook pages, birthday decorations, holiday cards, invitations, T-shirts, hats and jeans, and the list goes on and on!

Small, medium and border-sized Originals dies can be used in the SophistiCut™, Big Shot™, BIGkick™, Vagabond™ and original Sizzix® machines.

name: Sizzix PaddlePunch
description: Go where no punch has gone before. No longer are punches limited to where an ordinary paper punch can reach. PaddlePunch® Positionable Hand Punches can punch a decorative shape anywhere - including the center - of almost any flat craft project or crafting material. PaddlePunches can cut paper, cardstock, foil, thin rubber, fabric, felt, vinyl, vellum and printable magnet sheets.

name: Sizzix Paper Leather Sheets
description: It's the durable material that can do it all! Made from a latex saturated flat base to simulate the look and feel of real leather, Sizzix Paper Leather Sheets can be used to die-cut, emboss, print, ink, stitch, paint, watercolor, foil, collage or distress. Whether you wash it or use it in your printer, Paper Leather Sheets always retain their shape for a wide variety of uses. Use paper Leather to add dimension and texture to your next cardmaking, gift tag, home décor or sewing project.

name: Sizzix Paper Punches
description:
Easily embellish and enhance any creative task with the first Sizzix Paper Punches. Sizzix Paper Punches make amazing shapes for any occasion and can cut up to three sheets of cardstock, as well as fabric, fiber, foam, magnet, metallic foil, photographs, sandpaper (in limited use) and vellum.

Each Paper Punch is ergonomically designed with special comfort grip and locking latch for stackable storage. It includes a large surface area for the most exact cutting and leverage.

name: Sizzix Pop 'n Cuts Magnetic Insert Dies
description:
Pop goes the die-cut! When a Pop 'n Cuts™ Magnetic Insert Die is combined with a Pop 'n Cuts Base Die, you can create impressive 3-D pop-up cards in just a few quick steps. Simply pop the insert into place, lining up the center crease marks and die-cut for an incredibly easy shape-cutting experience!

Pop 'n Cuts Magnetic Dies can be used independently in the Movers & Shapers™ Base Tray. Select combinations of Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies and Pop 'n Cuts can be used to create decorative windows within the pop-up shape. Pop 'n Cuts are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines. For more information, watch these videos: An Introduction, Using with Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies, Using with the Base Tray.

name: Sizzix Pop 'n Cuts XL Dies
description:
Pop goes the die-cut! When a Pop 'n Cuts™ Magnetic Insert Die is combined with a Pop 'n Cuts Base Die, you can create impressive 3-D pop-up cards in just a few quick steps. Simply pop the insert into place, lining up the center crease marks and die-cut for an incredibly easy shape-cutting experience!

Select combinations of Movers & Shapers™ Magnetic Dies and Pop 'n Cuts can be used to create decorative windows within the pop-up shape. Pop 'n Cuts XL Dies are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines. For more information, watch these videos: An Introduction, Using with Movers & Shapers Magnetic Dies.

name: Sizzix Rub Ons
description: For a neat idea made from scratch, Rub Ons easily transfer onto a variety of surfaces. In many cases, these quick embellishments match and enhance specific Sizzlits® designs. Of course, Rub Ons offer infinite options to create a stir all by themselves.

name: Sizzix ScoreBoards Dies
description:
If it's chipboard or matboard, then ScoreBoards™ dies expand your creativity with quick and easy cuts and scoring. The first-ever product of its kind, ScoreBoards dies produce sturdier boxes, pockets, holders and other ultra-versatile designs.

These ScoreBoards dies showcase the novel style of Matboard Magic author Eileen Hull®. ScoreBoards easily cut and score most matboard and chipboard. Fun assembly required! (Use board thickness from .040" to .055" for best results.)

name: Sizzix ScoreBoards L Dies
description:
If it's chipboard or matboard, then ScoreBoards™ L dies expand your creativity with quick and easy cuts and scoring. The first-ever product of its kind, ScoreBoards L dies produce sturdier boxes, pockets, holders and other ultra-versatile designs.

These ScoreBoards L dies showcase the novel style of Matboard Magic author Eileen Hull®. ScoreBoards L dies easily cut and score most matboard and chipboard. Fun assembly required! (Use board thickness from .040" to .055" for best results.)

name: Sizzix ScoreBoards Pro Dies
description:
If it's chipboard or matboard, then ScoreBoards™ Pro Dies expand your creativity with quick and easy cuts and scoring. The first-ever product of its kind, ScoreBoards Pro Dies produce sturdier boxes, pockets, holders and other ultra-versatile designs.

These ScoreBoards Pro Dies showcase the novel style of Matboard Magic author Eileen Hull®. ScoreBoards Pro Dies easily cut and score most matboard and chipboard. Fun assembly required! (Use board thickness from .040" to .055" for best results.)

name: Sizzix ScoreBoards XL Dies
description:
If it's chipboard or matboard, then ScoreBoards™ XL Dies expand your creativity with quick and easy cuts and scoring. The first-ever product of its kind, ScoreBoards XL Dies produce sturdier boxes, pockets, holders and other ultra-versatile designs.

These ScoreBoards XL Dies showcase the novel style of Matboard Magic author Eileen Hull®. ScoreBoards XL Dies easily cut and score most matboard and chipboard. Fun assembly required! (Use board thickness from .040" to .055" for best results.)

name: Sizzix ShadowPress
description:
Hard pressed for what to say? With ShadowPress™ Debossing Folders, you'll always have just the right words to create a visual debossed sentiment. Each impression mimics the look of letterpress designs on cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum. For added visual effects, use inks, markers or other color tools to fill in the negative space of the shadows and make a bolder impression!

ShadowPress are compatible with the Texture Boutique™ (used with a pair of Embossing Pads), BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ Machines (used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform).

name: Sizzix Sidekick Machine
description:
With a few turns of its handle, the Sidekick® cuts single sheets of lightweight paper to cardstock and transforms them into something special. The Sidekick works with the entire Sizzix® Sizzlits® product library (with the exception of large Sizzlits dies) - and that includes our small dies to our 12" long Sizzlits Decorative Strip dies.

If that wasn't impressive enough, the portable, affordable and adorable roller machine also elegantly embosses with Textured Impressions™ Embossing Folders (small only). The handy vacuum seal attaches to most work surfaces for creativity anywhere. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards, invitations, scrapbook pages and much more! (To ensure compatibility, always check machine and accessory requirements.)

name: Sizzix Simple Impressions
description:
Ah, the elegance of embossed invitations, greeting cards, stationery, place cards, decorations and more. But who has the time to make them?

It's time to raise your creative expectations! Simple Impressions® Embossing Folders make embossing quicker and easier than ever. Simply place the stencil and cardstock, paper, metallic foil, or vellum to be embossed inside the folder and your Sizzix® machine* does the rest. Keep using them, and you'll be impressed every time!

*Most Simple Impressions work in the entire family of Sizzix machines, but some are compatible with roller machines only (where noted).

name: Sizzix Sizzlits Decorative Strip Dies
description:
Looking for something different? Take a long look at Sizzlits® Decorative Strip Dies*.

With a beautiful edge-to-edge appeal, these extended length dies make all sorts of extra-long shapes from colorful cardstock - including majestic borders for cards and scrapbook pages, snazzy decos for frames and mats as well as wonderful wrappers for candy bars! Just use your imagination with a Sizzix® roller machine and you'll go a long way!

*Decorative Strip dies are for roller machines only.

name: Sizzix Sizzlits Dies (Large)
description: Designed to cut a single sheet of cardstock in larger Sizzix® roller machines, Sizzlits® create fabulous shapes that make a great big difference with your papercrafting. Whenever you need a cute little shape, Sizzlits answer your inspiration! Choose from truly dazzling decorative sets, singles and alphabets that celebrate your unique artistry with an unmatched flair for fun!

name: Sizzix Sizzlits Dies (Small & Medium)
description:
Designed to cut a single sheet of cardstock in most Sizzix® machines*, Sizzlits® create fabulous little shapes that make a great big difference with your papercrafting. Whenever you need a cute little shape, Sizzlits answer your inspiration! Choose from truly dazzling decorative sets, singles and alphabets that celebrate your unique artistry with an unmatched flair for fun!

*Many Sizzlits work in the entire family of Sizzix machines, but some are compatible with roller machines only (where noted).

name: Sizzix SophistiCut Machine
description: Easy and elegant, the Sizzix® SophistiCut™ Die-Cutting Machine sports a stylish purse design with a 3" wide opening to accommodate small, medium and border-sized Sizzix Originals™ dies. The machine cuts a wide range of materials - everything from cardstock to fabric. The SophistiCut features a fold-out working platform, durable rollers and a large, easy-to-turn side handle. With the SophistiCut, charming shapes can be easily created for appliqué, home décor, fashion, jewelry, altered art, cardmaking, scrapbooking and many more crafts. (To ensure compatibility, always check accessory requirements.)

name: Sizzix TalkingTag Labels
description: Connecting the story behind your most treasured creations, TalkingTag Labels literally lend a recorded voice to any fabric project. After downloading a free TalkingTag app to any smart phone, simply scan the tag and record up to one minute of personalized audio. (For playback, scan the tag again from any smart phone and retrieve the voice recording from a secured platform.) Attach the tag and hear your creation come to life! For more information, watch this video: Using TalkingTag Message and Memory Labels.

name: Sizzix Texture Boutique Machine
description:
Resembling an ornate purse with a beaded handle, the Texture Boutique™ transforms ordinary cardstock into elegant embossed art. The Texture Boutique works with the Sizzix Textured Impressions™, Texture Fades™ and Texture Trades™ embossing folder product library (up to 4 1/2" wide).

If that wasn't impressive enough, the portable and affordable roller machine goes beyond cardstock to emboss paper, metallic foil, vellum and other thin materials. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards or invitations for any occasion and use the embellishments to add a special touch to your scrapbook pages, home décor projects, altered art, and much more! (To ensure compatibility, always check machine and accessory requirements.)

name: Sizzix Texture Fades
description:
Distress to impress! Texture Fades™ Embossing Folders easily emboss in such a way that select areas of the image appear perfectly faded and distressed. You can turn ordinary cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum into an embossed, textured masterpiece. The large folder fits the exact dimensions of an A2 card.

Texture Fades Embossing Folders are compatible with the Texture Boutique™ (when used with a pair of Embossing Pads), BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ Machines only (used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform).

name: Sizzix Texture Trades
description:
Sized perfectly for artist trading cards, Texture Trades™ offer all the altered appeal that creative types need to make a great impression - and then some! Use them to turn ordinary cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum into an embossed, textured masterpiece.

Texture Trades Embossing Folders are compatible with the Texture Boutique™ (when used with a pair of Embossing Pads), BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ Machines only (used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform).

name: Sizzix Textured Impressions
description:
Create a big impression! Textured Impressions™ Embossing Folders offer our deepest and boldest embossing experience yet. With just one embossing folder, you can turn ordinary cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum into an embossed, textured masterpiece. The large folder in the Textured Impressions Sets fits the exact dimensions of an A2 or A6 card cover, while the small, medium or border sizes create amazing embellishments.

Textured Impressions Embossing Folder Sets are compatible with the Texture Boutique™ (when used with a pair of Embossing Pads), BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ Machines only (when used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform).

name: Sizzix Textured Impressions 6" x 6"
description:
Create a big impression! Textured Impressions™ Embossing Folders offer our deepest and boldest embossing experience yet. With just one embossing folder, you can turn ordinary cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum into an embossed, textured masterpiece. The folder fits the exact dimensions of many different craft materials readily available in the 6" x 6" size.

Textured Impressions 6" x 6" Embossing Folders are compatible with the BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ Machines only (when used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform).

name: Sizzix Textured Impressions Plus
description:
Create an even bigger impression! Textured Impressions™ Plus Embossing Folders offer our deepest and boldest embossing experience yet. With just one embossing folder, you can turn ordinary cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum into an embossed, textured masterpiece.

Measuring 8 1/4" x 11 3/4" x 1/8", Textured Impressions Plus Embossing Folders are compatible with the Big Shot™ Plus and Big Shot Pro machines (used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's Platform System). All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Textured Impressions Pro
description:
Make a great big beautiful impression! Our 13" x 12 3/8" x 1/4" Textured Impressions™ Pro Embossing Folders add texture to your larger-sized creations such as scrapbook page backgrounds, full-size bags, boxes, cards, envelopes and album covers. On opposite sides of a hinged plastic folder, a positive plastic surface nests into a negative plastic surface and creates a sandwich for your cardstock, metallic foil, paper or vellum to be easily embossed.

Textured Impressions Pro Embossing Folders are only compatible with the Big Shot™ Pro Machine. (To ensure compatibility, always check machine and accessory requirements. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Sizzix Textured Impressions w/Stamp
description:
Create a big impression! Textured Impressions™ Embossing Folders offer our deepest and boldest embossing experience yet. With just one embossing folder, you can turn ordinary cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum into an embossed, textured masterpiece. Packaged with a stylish, complementary cling rubber stamp, this pack of Textured Impressions Embossing Folders combines two exciting forms of creativity for a raised 3-D design.

Textured Impressions Embossing Folders are compatible with the Texture Boutique™ (when used with a pair of Embossing Pads), BIGkick™, Big Shot™ and Vagabond™ Machines only (when used with a pair of Cutting Pads and the machine's included Platform).

name: Sizzix Texturz Accessories
description:
When you're ready to use your Texturz™ Texture Plates in your BIGkick™, Big Shot™, Vagabond™ or Big Shot Pro machine, there's a few Texturz Accessories* you'll need.

In order to add texture to thin material surfaces such as paper, cardstock and foil, you'll need an Impressions Pad to maintain the proper pressure and height necessary for texturizing, as well as Silicone Rubber to help make a lasting impression. For added versatility, use Impressions Pad and Silicone Rubber to emboss with any metal stencil.

*Impressions Pad and Silicone Rubber are included as part of Texturz Starter Kit. Both require the use of your machine's included platform.

name: Sizzix Texturz Plate Sets
description:
For more design options beyond the Texturz™ Starter Kit, our Texturz Plate Sets are equally impressive! This stylish selection of textured patterns and designs transforms paper, cardstock, metallic foil and other thin surfaces into impressive masterpieces.

Breathtaking gift wraps, tags, boxes, bags and frames are only the surface of what's possible! Each kit features three double-sided Texture Plates for a total of six distinctive designs.

name: Sizzix Texturz Starter Kits
description:
Everything you need to transform paper, cardstock and other thin surfaces into impressive masterpieces is right here in one place! A Texturz™ Starter Kit features three double-sided Texture Plates for a total of six distinctive designs. Also included are an Impressions Pad* to maintain the proper pressure and height necessary for texturizing, as well as Silicone Rubber* to help make a lasting impression.

Breathtaking gift wraps, tags, boxes, bags and frames are only the surface of what's possible! For added versatility, use Impressions Pad and Silicone Rubber to emboss with any metal stencil.

*Impressions Pad and Silicone Rubber are for use in larger Sizzix® roller machines and require the use of your machine's included platform.

name: Sizzix Thinlits Die Sets
description: Thinlits™ create dazzling detailed shapes for more creative cardmaking and papercrafting projects. These wafer-thin chemical-etched die sets are designed to cut a single sheet of cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum. They are simple to use, compact and portable for cutting at home or on the go. Use them for enhanced intricacy and to add a special touch of inspiration to all your projects. For use in the larger Sizzix® roller machines with the machine's included platform; when using the Essentials Platform or Solo Platform & Shim, the Extended Adapter or Solo Adapter is required. All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Thinlits Die Sets w/Textured Impressions
description: The combination of a Thinlits™ Die Set and Textured Impressions™ Embossing Folder Set allows you to create the most exact cuts around your embossed images. These wafer-thin, chemical-etched die sets feature the perfect registration without interference from any ridges at the edge of the die opening. Designed to cut a single sheet of cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum, these dies also make great stencils. For use in the larger Sizzix® roller machines with the machine's included platform; when using the Essentials Platform or Solo Platform & Shim, the Extended Adapter or Solo Adapter is required. All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Thinlits Plus Die Sets
description: Thinlits™ create dazzling detailed shapes for more creative cardmaking and papercrafting projects. These wafer-thin chemical-etched die sets are designed to cut a single sheet of cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum. They are simple to use, compact and portable for cutting at home or on the go. Use them for enhanced intricacy and to add a special touch of inspiration to all your projects. For use in the Sizzix® Big Shot™ Plus or Big Shot Pro machines. All items sold separately.

name: Sizzix Triplits Die Sets
description:
Mix, match, layer or stack. With Triplits™ Dies, the creative combinations are endless! These dazzling detailed shapes are ideal for all your cardmaking and papercrafting projects. Taking your creativity further, these wafer-thin chemical-etched die sets are designed to cut a single sheet of cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum. Use them for enhanced intricacy and to add a special touch of inspiration to all your projects.

Triplits Dies are compatible with Big Shot™, BIGkick™ and Vagabond™ Machines with the machine's included platform; when using the Essentials Platform or Solo Platform & Shim, the Extended Adapter or Solo Adapter is required. For more information, watch this video: Using Triplits Dies.

name: Sizzix Vagabond Machine
description:
Resembling a well-traveled suitcase on the outside, the Vagabond™ Machine easily opens up to reveal a powerful machine that takes you to imaginative new places. With just the push of a button, the Vagabond leaves the crank behind. The motorized Vagabond works with the entire Sizzix® product library (with the exception of Bigz™ Plus and Bigz Pro dies) - and that includes our smallest dies to our big 6" wide plastic-backed treasures and embossing tools.

If that wasn't enough, this portable roller machine cuts and embosses many different materials. Create your own one-of-a-kind cards, invitations, scrapbook pages, home décor, fashion, altered art, quilting and much more! (To ensure compatibility, always check accessory requirements. Machine accessories may be sold separately.)

name: Double Cut Crease Die w/Large Flap
Die Storage
description:
Whether you're taking your Sizzix stuff on the road or just want to keep it neat and organized at home, storage solutions uniquely suit your lifestyle.

Designed specifically for your dies, these storage items stylishly protect your prized possessions.

name: Machine Sets
description: Whether you're reinforcing lessons, promoting hands-on activities or just decorating your next themed bulletin board, Ellison shape-cutting machines create the perfect applications to meet your important standards. Ideal for the classroom and home school environments, our machines are easy-to-operate and cut many different materials for countless curriculum-based shapes. Use them to enhance any subject, while increasing retention and making learning fun!

name: Die-Cutting Machines
description: From wedding invitations and decorations to making memories of your last vacation last a little longer, Sizzix die-cutting machines truly empower your creativity.Our growing family of award-winning Sizzix machines are available in different sizes, options and capabilities to fit any size imagination. For more information, watch this video: Choosing Your Sizzix Machine.

name: Electronic Shape-Cutting Machines
description:
With no cartridges required, the newly redesigned eclips2 DIY Electronic Cutter contains an enhanced motor with industrial-strength gears for speed, reduced noise, efficiency, precision cutting and more. In addition, the eclips2 is accompanied by free eCAL lite software to create your own designs, plus cut, score and draw/edit unique shapes for beautiful customized projects from the start.

With the eclips2 and eCAL lite, you can weld multiple shapes and letters into one cut. Use Appearance Styles, like Shadow and Blackout, to quickly change the look of letters and shapes. You can also access TrueType, OpenType and fonts currently installed on your computer, including Dingbat/Wingding fonts.

name: Embossing Machines
description:
From wedding invitations and decorations to making memories of your last vacation last a little longer, Sizzix embossing machines truly empower your creativity.

Our growing family of award-winning Sizzix machines are available in different sizes, options and capabilities to fit any size imagination. For more information, watch this video: Choosing Your Sizzix Machine.

name: Idea Books
description: Take a major you-turn! The Sizzix Idea Book: Make It Your Style is your inspiring resource for exploring our most popular Sizzix products. Each project features a step-by-step guide to many of the exciting tips and techniques used by the Sizzix design team. From personal fashion and home décor to papercrafting, scrapbooking and more, the Sizzix Idea Book is 116 pages filled with inspiring ideas designed to spark your personal flair for creativity.

name: Machine Accessories
description:
Looking for a replacement part or just want to take your creativity further? Either way, you've come to the right place.

Whatever your creative challenge, if it's made for a Sizzix machine, you can find it here!

name: Machine Storage
description:
Whether you're taking your Sizzix stuff on the road or just want to keep it neat and organized at home, Sizzix storage solutions uniquely suit your lifestyle.

Take a tote or two on your travels! They prominently feature the Sizzix logo and stylishly protect your prized Sizzix possessions.

name: Classroom Series
description: Class is now in session for the Sizzix Classroom Series. This must-have collection of Sizzix Dies and eclips cartridges boldly creates a multitude of engaging shapes to empower learning in the classroom and beyond. Ideal for any teacher, tutor or parent motivating students to succeed, each shape enhances creative arts & crafts as well as many other subject areas to make every discovery amazing!

name: Education Collection
description:
This collection of dies was specifically designed with education in mind, whether it is for classroom displays, reward charts, learning tools, after school clubs and more. The designs stem from 1977 when the Ellison Education brand was first created to save teachers time in preparing lessons, inspire exciting subject topics with projects and make lessons more engaging for students.

The dies in this collection are ideal for creating tactile learning displays as they cut not only paper and card, but also felt, fabric, craft metal, shrink plastic, balsa wood, hessian, leather and much more. If you have any questions regarding the range or would like information on ordering, please contact our Customer Service team.

name: Machines
description: Whether youre reinforcing lessons, promoting hands-on activities or just decorating your next themed bulletin board, Ellison shape-cutting machines create the perfect applications to meet your important standards. Ideal for the classroom and home school environments, our machines are easy-to-operate and cut many different materials for countless curriculum-based shapes. Use them to enhance any subject, while increasing retention and making learning fun!
